- 'prolonged period' of time: refers to more than 180 days since the last service;
- 'alive' average voltage and current values: refers to values greater than 0.

sql:
SELECT AVG(capacity) AS average_capacity
FROM battery_cells
WHERE warranty_expiry_date > '2023-12-31';
